      <t>This document describes a new Remote Authentication Dial-In User Service (RADIUS) attribute, Chargeable-User-Identity.  This attribute can be used by a home network to identify a user for the purpose of roaming transactions that occur outside of the home network. [STANDARDS-TRACK]
